body:
A forge vanilla-friendly mod that adds 4 new tools that can be crafted from iron, gold, diamond, and netherite.
Made a fabric version, you can find it in the files.
The current version is for 1.20.1.

Current content:
- Tool handle, necessary item to craft the new tools;
- Hammer, same damage as a sword, faster mining speed with additional knockback;
- Great axe, faster chopping speed with more damage but low attack speed;
- Knife, high attack speed with low damage;
- Mace, same damage as sword and applies slowness to mobs;


Compatible with my other mods:
- Bronze Armor: use the bronze ingot for the recipes,
- Smithing Steel: upgrade iron tools with a steel ingot on a smithing table, also unlocks a recipe for the hammer,


Notes:
- Smelting bronze or steel tools will give iron nuggets instead of their respective material. I will try to change in the future;

Check the images for more information.

Feel free to use it on your modpack, just make sure to credit it and don't claim it as your own.
Have fun!
